casebody.data:
TORREY, Respondent v. TORREY, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by Owen Torrey against David Torrey.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Motion to strike case from the calendar, and for affirmance, granted on default, with costs.
